'''Hau polyps''' were an organic material used by the [[Yuuzhan Vong]] as seats and mobile cushions. Constantly pulsing, they were made of fiberous red material. [[Supreme Overlord]] [[Shimrra Jamaane|Shimrra]] had a [[Polyp throne|huge throne]] in [[Shimrra's Citadel|his Citadel]] made of hau polyps, and a polyp would occasionally burst due to his massive size.

